        "authorId" : "bb5f3442-a604-42a4-a77a-2008548cc43d",
        "body" : "Then it's best to set it to one host.\r\n\r\nI would also recommend to keep it simple (the Ansible way) and replace this dictionary with a simple list (e.g. `opennebula_test_hosts`). ",
